xt\": \"Pan American Games\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pan_American_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pan_American_Games\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an individual dressage spot\", \"from\": 158, \"to\": 185}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Paris Olympic Games\", \"from\": 189, \"to\": 217}, {\"ngram\": \"virtue\", \"from\": 221, \"to\": 227}, {\"ngram\": \"its home\", \"from\": 281, \"to\": 289}, {\"ngram\": \"October\", \"from\": 317, \"to\": 324}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the country has now been bumped from the spot.\", \"from\": 329, \"to\": 379, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 333, \"to\": 344}, {\"ngram\": \"the spot\", \"from\": 370, \"to\": 378}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Brazil, which secured an Olympic team dressage place with its silver medal at the Pan American Games, was unable to submit the National Olympic Committee (NOC) certificate of capabilityby the 5 January deadline (news, 18 January).\", \"from\": 381, \"to\": 611, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 381, \"end\": 387, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\", \"score\": 0.8576944356865736, \"rank\": 0.16573721697229435, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\"}, {\"begin\": 463, \"end\": 481, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pan_American_Games\", \"score\": 0.9731364806228177, \"rank\": 0.01446404796342366, \"text\": \"Pan American Games\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pan_American_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pan_American_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 508, \"end\": 540, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"National Olympic Committee (NOC)\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an Olympic team\", \"from\": 403, \"to\": 418}, {\"ngram\": \"dressage place\", \"from\": 419, \"to\": 433}, {\"ngram\": \"its silver medal\", \"from\": 439, \"to\": 455}, {\"ngram\": \"capabilityby\", \"from\": 556, \"to\": 568}, {\"ngram\": \"the 5 January deadline\", \"from\": 569, \"to\": 591}, {\"ngram\": \"news\", \"from\": 593, \"to\": 597}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Brazil was then entitled to one individual quota place instead and that quota place had to come from within FEI Olympic groups D&E (North America & Central and South America) as per the qualification system,\\\" an FEI spokesperson toldH&H.\", \"from\": 613, \"to\": 851, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 614, \"end\": 620, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\", \"score\": 0.8576944356865736, \"rank\": 0.16573721697229435, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\"}, {\"begin\": 722, \"end\": 725, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.092370260378041e-35, \"text\": \"FEI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 826, \"end\": 829, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.092370260378041e-35, \"text\": \"FEI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one individual quota place\", \"from\": 642, \"to\": 668}, {\"ngram\": \"quota place\", \"from\": 686, \"to\": 697}, {\"ngram\": \"D&E\", \"from\": 741, \"to\": 744}, {\"ngra