ce/Chilean_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1510, \"end\": 1517, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile\", \"score\": 0.9999825054990278, \"rank\": 1.7482639597209573e-05, \"text\": \"Chilean\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a joint statement\", \"from\": 1548, \"to\": 1565}, {\"ngram\": \"March\", \"from\": 1569, \"to\": 1574}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They said that the FEI recently announced its decision to remove Chile from the individual quota place \\\"that it had legitimately obtained [\\u2026] through direct classification at the Santiago 2023 Pan American Games, and which had even been officially announced and published by the FEI\\\".\", \"from\": 1576, \"to\": 1860, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1595, \"end\": 1598, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.092370260378041e-35, \"text\": \"FEI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 1641, \"end\": 1646, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile\", \"score\": 0.9999903607845959, \"rank\": 9.63142020002586e-06, \"text\": \"Chile\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile\"}, {\"begin\": 1769, \"end\": 1787, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pan_American_Games\", \"score\": 0.9731364806228177, \"rank\": 0.01446404796342366, \"text\": \"Pan American Games\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pan_American_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pan_American_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 1855, \"end\": 1858, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.092370260378041e-35, \"text\": \"FEI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its decision\", \"from\": 1618, \"to\": 1630}, {\"ngram\": \"the individual quota place\", \"from\": 1652, \"to\": 1678}, {\"ngram\": \"direct classification\", \"from\": 1726, \"to\": 1747}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This decision - in our opinion - is not consistent with the rules and regulations of fair play and the principles of Olympic movement,\\\" said the statement.\", \"from\": 1862, \"to\": 2018, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This decision\", \"from\": 1863, \"to\": 1876}, {\"ngram\": \"our opinion\", \"from\": 1882, \"to\": 1893}, {\"ngram\": \"the rules\", \"from\": 1919, \"to\": 1928}, {\"ngram\": \"regulations\", \"from\": 1933, \"to\": 1944}, {\"ngram\": \"fair play\", \"from\": 1948, \"to\": 1957}, {\"ngram\": \"the principles\", \"from\": 1962, \"to\": 1976}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic movement\", \"from\": 1980, \"to\": 1996}, {\"ngram\": \"the statement\", \"from\": 2004, \"to\": 2017}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Due to the above, unfortunately we have no choice but to object said decision, to be rectified and adjusted to what should be a correct and harmonious application of the current rules, respecting Chile's right to have its individual quota for Paris 2024 duly recognised.\", \"from\": 2020, \"to\": 2291, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2217, \"end\": 2222, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile\", \"score\": 0.9999903607845959, \"rank\": 9.63142020002586e-06, \"text\": \"Chile\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile\"}, {\"begin\": 2264, \"end\": 2274, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.1880504713237567e-21, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no choice\", \"from\": 2061, \"to\": 2070}, {\"ngram\": \"said decision\", \"from\": 2085, \"to\": 2098}, {\"ngram\": \"a correct and harmonious application\", \"from\": 2147, \"to\": 2183}, {\"ngram\": \"the current rules\", \"from\": 2187, \"to\": 2204}, {\"ngram\": \"its individual quota\", \"from\": 2239, \"to\": 2259}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have kindly asked the FEI to reconsider its decision, as there are many arguments and precedents that support Chile's position, in order to restore Chile to the individual quota.\", \"from\": 2293, \"to\": 2475, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2319, \"end\": 2322, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.092370260378041e-35, \"text\": \"FEI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 2407, \"end\": 2412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile\", \"score\": 0.9999903607845959, \"rank\": 9.63142020002586e-06, \"text\": \"Chile\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile\"}, {\"begin\": 2445, \"end\": 2450, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile\", \"score\": 0.9999903607845959, \"rank\": 9.63142020002586e-06, \"text\": \"Chile\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its decision\", \"from\": 2337, \"to\": 2349}, {\"ngram\": \"many arguments\", \"from\": 2364, \"to\": 2378}, {\"ngram\": \"precedents\", \"from\": 2383, \"to\": 2393}, {\"ngram\": \"order\", \"from\": 2428, \"to\": 2433}, {\"ngram\": \"the individual quota\", \"from\": 2454, \"to\": 2474}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Notwithstanding, our country, if needed, will resort to all necessary international bodies to reverse this decision, which is clearly incorrect and unfair.\\\"\", \"from\": 2477, \"to\": 2634, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Notwithstanding\", \"from\": 2478, \"to\": 2493}, {\"ngram\": \"our country\", \"from\": 2495, \"to\": 2506}, {\"ngram\": \"all necessary international bodies\", \"from\": 2534, \"to\": 2568}, {\"ngram\": \"this decision\", \"from\": 2580, \"to\": 2593}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Chile's individual eventing place at this summer's Games has also been reallocated, owing to the sad loss of a horse.\", \"from\": 2636, \"to\": 2753, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2636, \"end\": 2641, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile\", \"score\": 0.9999903607845959, \"rank\": 9.63142020002586e-06, \"text\": \"Chile\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this summer's Games\", \"from\": 2673, \"to\": 2692}, {\"ngram\": \"the sad loss\", \"from\": 2729, \"to\": 2741}, {\"ngram\": \"a horse\", \"from\": 2745, \"to\": 2752}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite veterinary treatment, Ed\\u00e9n, an 11-year-old mare ridden by Jaime Bittner, died as a result of an internal infection.\", \"from\": 2755, \"to\": 2878, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2821, \"end\": 2826, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jaime_Hernandez\", \"score\": 0.9243375783426441, \"rank\": 0.08185583212240335, \"text\": \"Jaime\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jaime_Hernandez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jaime_Hernandez\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"veterinary treatment\", \"from\": 2763, \"to\": 2783}, {\"ngram\": \"Ed\\u00e9n\", \"from\"